{
  "stem": "7094.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There is this power for good and bad in each of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it depends which one wins, which one is projected or encouraged or-- or-- and I'm a firm believer that only through education can you do it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I'm now very much converted to art.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I think that art has got a great inference to play in-- in-- in bringing up a better world.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I know science-- we have so many fallen idols on the way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Also, I had a very scientific background, and I was educated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, if you saw the consequences of scientific effort in the camps, you just realize how dangerous science can be.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, just that I love them very much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That I hope that they'll remember-- that they will continue the way they are.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that they will-- I see in Daniel a great interest, really, and David, as they're growing up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They want to know, and so I'm encouraged by that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that they will have a fulfilled life, that they will grow up as nice as they are doing now, that they'll be nice human beings.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's very important for me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, more or less I think I mentioned it that-- that very often in these memories, I hope that I don't-- that I represent a generation, that I don't talk only about myself.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because whether I was lucky or unlucky, survived, that-- you know, if somebody said, oh, aren't you lucky you survived?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, sometimes it's like a knife into-- what is the luck to survive if you just survived on your own?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is not great luck in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think the-- the-- the consequences of the survival afterwards are just as grim, as terrible, as this process of surviving sometimes.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
